   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="Edgeworth_Huntington_F15153_1845_05_16_page01.jpg"/>
            <p> <persName ref="./Personography.xml#EdgeM1">Miss Edgeworth</persName> understands<lb/>
               from <persName ref="./Personography.xml#HervX1">D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>. H<unclear>erve</unclear></persName> of <placeName ref="./Placeography.xml#Boston_MA_US">Boston</placeName> that<lb/>
               he has sent the 13<hi rend="superscript">th</hi>. Report of<lb/>
               the <placeName ref="./Placeography.xml#Perkins-School_MA_US">Perkins Instruction for<lb/>
                  the Blind</placeName> to Mess<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>. <persName ref="./Personography.xml#WileX1">Wiley</persName> &amp; <persName ref="./Personography.xml#PickX1">Pick<unclear>ram</unclear></persName><lb/>
               for her— She requests that they<lb/>
               will be so good as to send it<lb/>
               for her to care of <persName ref="./Personography.xml#WilsL1"><choice><orig>L.</orig><reg>Lestock</reg></choice> <choice><orig>P.</orig><reg>Peach</reg></choice> Wilson</persName> Esq<lb/>
               <placeName ref="./Placeography.xml#North-Audley-Street-1_ENK">1 North Audley Street</placeName><lb/>
</p>
            <closer>
               <dateline>
                  <placeName ref="./Placeography.xml#Edgeworthstown_IE">Edgeworthstown</placeName><lb/>
                  <date when="1845-05-16"/>  16. May .45<lb/>
